        "action": "Require schools and exam boards to allow students to use the internet for exams",
        "additional_details": "In real life most people have access to the internet, so we don't see why students should have to remember facts and equations for exams, when they can find these using the internet.",
        "background": "We want the Government to make it so students are allowed to use the internet for research during exams.",
